including a first shot at defining noninterference modulo declassification.  I have included definitions for release policies using equivalence relations that are characteried by syntactic formulas in our logic, and defined what these mean in a multi-trace setting.  I have then stated noninterference modulo declassificiation up to this relation, and then I have written the "what" formula in our logic that corresponds to this property and put a theorem asserting their equivalence in our appendix.  Next I have to do the proof of the equivalence.
